Image::OCR::Tesseract
=====================

You will need tesseract and ImageMagick installed on your system.
This package runs on Unix/Linux type OS.

The Makefile.PL will check that you have tesseract installed.


INSTALLING TESSERACT
====================

Installing tesseract can be tricky.
You will basically need gcc-c++ and automake installed on your system.

You may be able to simply install the SVN version of Tesseract by using:

 svn checkout http://tesseract-ocr.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ tesseract-ocr
 ./runautoconf
 mkdir build-directory
 cd build-directory
 ../configure
 make
 make install


for more see google project on ocr, they use tesseract






